WRITING.TITLE: FILD issues
WRITING.TEXT: Hey, so a few days ago I just found out about FILD, and the following night I was woken up by my dog, so I thought it was the ideal time to try out FILD. I have wanted to try it again, but using my alarm. The problem with this is that I move too much and I can't FILD, I have been looking for an app that either has a huge dismiss button or that turns off automatically after 20 seconds or something, basically something that allows for minimal movement. I would be interested to know how other people wake themselves up without moving too much. Thanks!

Well, I once lucid dreamt without even doing an rc or anything, I just suddenly bursted out saying "IM HAVING A LUCID DREAM!!!" I basically told everyone that I was dreaming, and most people replied with "yes... yes you are" as they were smiling, it was like I was the idiot who didn't realise what was happening. That was pretty cool.
I was going to make it into a GIF, but I put it on YouTube, so I didn't see the point.
